    "Need to point out why a student made a specific error and how they can avoid this in the future.",
    "With a large class, it is difficult to provide a deep level of feedback with allowable marking time.",
    "AI may enable this by providing detail feedback in a short period of time.",
    "Seven participants (36.8%) indicated that effective feedback centres on several key factors such as being clear, specific, constructive and encouraging, and serving as a tool for improvement not just critique.",
    "Participants regarded it as essential for students to know what they did wrong and how they could correct it in the future."
